          /*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
          Function:       footnoteLinks()
          Author:         Aaron Gustafson (aaron at easy-designs dot net)
          Creation Date:  8 May 2005
          Version:        1.3
          Homepage:       http://www.easy-designs.net/code/footnoteLinks/
